HEADWORD: Inutility
<hw>In`u*til"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inutilitas</ets>: cf. F. <ets>inutilit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Uselessness; the quality of being unprofitable; unprofitableness;
<as>as, the <ex>inutility</ex> of vain speculations and visionary
projects</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inutterable</ent>⟦br⟧
